My friends and enemies. It's time for tyre thermals and tyre wear![/B]
Let me introduce you to the first publicly available mod that provides both tyre thermals and tyre wear!
Have you ever felt like doing a burnout didn't destroy your tyres enough? Have you ever thought "wow, wouldn't it be cool if I had to manage my tyre wear"? No? Well fear not, this mod is still a great option for you! With the extra realism this mod adds, you can finally satisfy that inner simrace-nerd in you.

[CENTER][IMG]https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1104452581675237396/1123561859790946304/image.png[/IMG]
[I]Reworked UI from v1.0.1

[MEDIA=youtube]_VdeqLUeHCg[/MEDIA]
[I]Showcase video for v0.1 by [USER=477185]@bowtiedylan[/USER][/I][/I][/CENTER]


[B][U]Mod features:[/U][/B]
- [B]Multiplayer compatible[/B];
- Tyre thermals based on several factors (such as tyre slip and load);
- Tyre wear based on similar factors, and the tyre thermals;
- 4 temperature zones (inner, center, outer and core);
- Dynamic tyre grip based on thermals and wear;
- Support for various compounds (standards, sports and race tyres);

[B][U]Known issues:[/U][/B]
- Tyres don't burst yet from their wear being too low;

[B][U]Upcoming features:[/U][/B]
- Wet tyre support;
- Hard/medium/soft compound support;
- Accompanying BeamMP plugin for pitstops/tire swaps;
- Bursting tyres with low tyre wear (WIP because BeamMP desync);

