[U]Changelog:[/U]
v1.2: Broken/deflated wheels now show up as 0% in the UI app. Tyre width now contributes to the overall calculation, fixing the behaviour for lightweight cars with small tyres and vice versa;
v1.1: Forced brake temps to default to environment temperature if they can't be read. Fixes bug with AI and wheels without brakes;
v1.0.1: The big release! UI reworked, behaviour entirely retuned and wheel core temperatures added;
v0.4: Major hotfix to a groundmodel related bug, which ruined v0.2 and v0.3;
v0.3: 3 ring temperature system, treaded tyre support and overall improvement to behaviour.
v0.2: Improved overall feel of the system and fixed most issues with overheating on slippery surfaces.
v0.1: Alpha/experimental version uploaded.

